e xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ohe1665702709579.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ohe1665702709579.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ohe1665702709579.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ohe1665702709579\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Text\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The text of the message, help text, language setup, panel or other global object.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ohe1665702709579__section_w1887ab1b5b1_w1888ab1b5_w1889ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ohe1665702709579__table_d12989e1_d12990e1_d12991e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Technical Name:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n                           \n                                   UTEXT</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Expected Value:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">String of Unicode characters.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Default Value:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ohe1665702709579__section_y2b_x3r_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d919150e114\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ohe1665702709579__ul_jjc_y3r_cxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ohe1665702709579__li_d42665e1_d42666e1_d42667e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vqz1665702709424.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vqz1665702709424.html\" title=\"A Menu is a Development Object that defines a Uniface menu bar, dropdown menu, or pop-up menu for a desktop application. It is cannot be used in web applications.\">Menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ohe1665702709579__li_d42668e1_d42669e1_d42670e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pdp1665702709496.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pdp1665702709496.html\" title=\"A Message is a Development Object that defines text to be used in the application, such as a label, help text, prompt, or error message.\">Message</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ohe1665702709579__li_d42671e1_d42672e1_d42673e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"luj1665702709292.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/luj1665702709292.html\" title=\"A Help Text is a legacy Development Object that defines a block of text that is displayed in an application window to provide help about the application. They are unlikely to be used in modern applications.\">Help Text</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ohe1665702709579__li_d42674e1_d42675e1_d42676e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wmu1665702708557.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wmu1665702708557.html\" title=\"A Drag-and-Drop Format is Development Object that defines a default action, pop-up menu, and icon that can be used when performing drag-and-drop actions in the tree and picture widgets of forms. It is not used for drag-and-drop widgets.\">Drag-and-Drop Format</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ohe1665702709579__li_d42677e1_d42678e1_d42679e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nub1705663388651.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nub1705663388651.html\" title=\"A language setup is a collection of definitions that specify the texts and formatting of language-related data that may be visible in the user interface of a desktop application.\">Language Setups</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hir1705568318852.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Messages</a><p>Messages are language-related objects that enable you to deploy a Uniface application in different languages and locales. They are stored in language-specific libraries, and Uniface automatically chooses the appropriate library at runtime based on the configuration.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swj1719500297780.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Drag-and-Drop Formats</a><p>Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614987\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614987\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Text Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Text The text of the message, help text, language setup, panel or other global object. Technical Name: UTEXT Expected Value: String of Unicode characters. Default Value: None Applies To Menu Message Help Text Drag-and-Drop Format Language Setups Related Links Messages Messages are language-related objects that enable you to deploy a Uniface application in different languages and locales. They are stored in language-specific libraries, and Uniface automatically chooses the appropriate library at runtime based on the configuration. Drag-and-Drop Formats Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}